column15: flowers are in bloom and the family picnic is around the corner. After months of waiting

column18:

Body

column19:
you look at it fondly and think of the next time you’ll take it out. It weighs 900 g and can be accommodated anywhere without any trouble. You have a tendency to misplace things and this backpack with a capacity of 22 L gives you the option to stuff anything you want into it. This backpack is an ideal travel bag as it features PES on the external and PA on the internal surface.

Features

column20: you all cheer in excitement. This is one of the best parts of the trip where everyone starts to sing and joke. Busy lives and schedules often get in the way but this is the one chance where you can make up for it all. After a fun-filled drive up to the spot

column22: you pick up your lightweight backpack and rush out. Run around and play catch in the open ground
column23:
after which you help your parents spread the blanket and arrange everything for lunch.

column25:
this backpack also comes with polyurethane and EVA padding. Go back home with memories to last you till the next trip.
